	(53,1,'2013-12-05 10:35:33','2013-12-05 10:35:33','<h1>Xmas Story</h1>\r\nYeah. Give a little credit to our public schools. You\'re going back for the Countess, aren\'t you? I decline the title of Iron Cook and accept the lesser title of Zinc Saucier, which I just made up. Uhh… also, comes with double prize money. Belligerent and numerous.\r\n<h2>The Day The Earth Stood Stupid</h2>\r\nBut I\'ve never been to the moon! Bender, hurry! This fuel\'s expensive! Also, we\'re dying! Please, Don-Bot… look into your hard drive, and open your mercy file! The key to victory is discipline, and that means a well made bed. You will practice until you can make your bed in your sleep. Does anybody else feel jealous and aroused and worried? For example, if you killed your grandfather, you\'d cease to exist!\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Oh sure! Blame the wizards!</li>\r\n	<li>Daylight and everything.</li>\r\n	<li>Fry! Stay back! He\'s too powerful!</li>\r\n	<li>For one beautiful night I knew what it was like to be a grandmother. Subjugated, yet honored.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Anthology of Interest I</h3>\r\nOkay, I like a challenge. Ooh, name it after me! The key to victory is discipline, and that means a well made bed. You will practice until you can make your bed in your sleep.\r\n<h4>Devil\'s Hands are Idle Playthings</h4>\r\nBender! Ship! Stop bickering or I\'m going to come back there and change your opinions manually! Tell her she looks thin. Okay, I like a challenge. I am the man with no name, Zapp Brannigan!\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Interesting. No, wait, the other thing: tedious.</li>\r\n	<li>For one beautiful night I knew what it was like to be a grandmother. Subjugated, yet honored.</li>\r\n	<li>Fatal.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h5>Mother\'s Day</h5>\r\nWhat kind of a father would I be if I said no? For one beautiful night I knew what it was like to be a grandmother. Subjugated, yet honored. As an interesting side note, as a head without a body, I envy the dead. Really?! Is the Space Pope reptilian!?','