	(54,1,'2013-07-19 13:16:25','2013-07-19 13:16:25','<h1>The Luck of the Fryrish</h1>\r\n<p>What kind of a father would I be if I said no? I didn\'t ask for a completely reasonable excuse! I asked you to get busy! I videotape every customer that comes in here, so that I may blackmail them later. Why, those are the Grunka-Lunkas! They work here in the Slurm factory.</p>\r\n<h2>Xmas Story</h2>\r\n<p>No. We\'re on the top. Spare me your space age technobabble, Attila the Hun! Then we\'ll go with that data file! Leela\'s gonna kill me. This is the worst part. The calm before the battle.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>That\'s the ONLY thing about being a slave.</li>\r\n<li>Oh, all right, I am. But if anything happens to me, tell them I died robbing some old man.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Bender Should Not Be Allowed on TV</h3>\r\n<p>Oh, all right, I am. But if anything happens to me, tell them I died robbing some old man. I guess because my parents keep telling me to be more ladylike. As though! I am Singing Wind, Chief of the Martians. Why am I sticky and naked? Did I miss something fun? When the lights go out, it\'s nobody\'s business what goes on between two consenting adults. I guess because my parents keep telling me to be more ladylike. As though!</p>\r\n<h4>Where the Buggalo Roam</h4>\r\n<p>We need rest.  The spirit is willing, but the flesh is spongy and bruised. Hey, you add a one and two zeros to that or we walk! I guess because my parents keep telling me to be more ladylike. As though!</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>This is the worst kind of discrimination: the kind against me!</li>\r\n<li>In your time, yes, but nowadays shut up! Besides, these are adult stemcells, harvested from perfectly healthy adults whom I killed for their stemcells.</li>\r\n<li>Switzerland is small and neutral! We are more like Germany, ambitious and misunderstood!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h5>Xmas Story</h5>\r\n<p>Kif might! Man, I\'m sore all over. I feel like I just went ten rounds with mighty Thor. We need rest.  The spirit is willing, but the flesh is spongy and bruised. Shinier than yours, meatbag. Leela, Bender, we\'re going grave robbing.</p>','Hello world!','','inherit','open','open','','1-revision-v1','','','2013-07-19 13:16:25','2013-07-19 13:16:25','',1,'http://192.168.1.32/barebones/1-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
